# RainDrop Web

## How to run

1. Install [.Net SDK 7](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet-core/7.0) for your PC
2. Run run.cmd (Windows), run.sh (Linux), ? (MacOS)
3. Open your browser and navigate to [here](http://localhost:10000)

## If you encounter an exception:

1. Go to [FTDI Driver Download Page](https://ftdichip.com/drivers/d2xx-drivers/) and find the driver for your OS.
2. Copy the library file here and replace the existing one (`ftdi2xx.dll`, `libftdi2xx.so`,
   or `libftdi2xx.dylib` (currently missing, for MacOS)).
3. Run and see if it goes well.

## 咋用

1. 到[.Net SDK 7](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet-core/7.0)下载安装Dotnet SDK环境 (理论上Runtime就行但我不会)
2. 在Windows下运行run.cmd, Linux下运行run.sh, Mac下我不知道应该也是run.sh
3. 打开浏览器到[这里](http://localhost:10000)

## 如果崩了

1. 到[FTDI Driver Download Page](https://ftdichip.com/drivers/d2xx-drivers/)找到适合你的系统版本的驱动程序
2. 拷贝到本目录下, 把原有的替换掉
3. 再试试
